For the TypeScript types, we can define the type of the `FeedScreen` component:

```tsx

type FeedParamList = {
  Latest: undefined;
  Popular: undefined;
};

// highlight-next-line
type Props = StaticScreenProps<NavigatorScreenParams<FeedParamList>>;

